{"tid":1804540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：新的一年帶來新的希望，願香港重新出發","createTime":"2019-12-31T05:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T06:35:52.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"072ea3d91f4ed6ebc09df685ee69ffd08719f4a1","tid":1804540,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥連同幾名司局長發表短片，回顧過去一年工作和提出新年希望。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，2019年香港經歷前所未有的嚴峻挑戰，因反修例而引起的社會動盪持續超過半年，大家很想盡快走出困局，市民面對這個情況覺得痛心、焦慮、失望，甚至憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，作為行政長官責無旁貸，她會虛心聆聽，為社會尋找出路，過程中堅守一國兩制原則、維護法治的核心價值。她承認，要香港穩步前行，政府除了處理面前的困難，也要承認制度上的不足，以及社會多年來積聚的深層次矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n她認為香港人過往憑毅力和智慧，安然渡過不少風浪，相信可以再一次克服困難、重建香港。她又說新的一年帶來新的希望，願社會早日復和、市民融洽相處、香港重新出發。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500293-20191231.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500293-20191231.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=7fe3053e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500293-20191231.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ae261d5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500293-20191231.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"399ea5eefef21a1a79011eee405b1cc1e7cf8a69","tid":1804540,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T05:27:10.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署 </ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=132a7932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?